A Safe Place 
Graphite on Bristol Board, 2019

A safe place, no matter if it is a place in your mind or a place you can physically visit, is a very important thing to have. We create these safe places throughout all of our childhood, in the woods, under the staircase, in our mind while daydreaming - but really, being a grown up is tough and really challenging, and I see people around me being stressed and anxious and constantly on the run, myself included! I came to the conclusion that EVERYONE needs a safe place! Make sure you find one for yourself and give it a visit on a regular base and stay for a little while!
